========================================================================
===================            NOTES               =====================
========================================================================

* tools/feedme.py lets you fill scrib's brain with text from a file.
* tools/twitter.py requires python-twyt
* There are soem other in-dev tools that use PHP to feed scrib some
  naughtiness in a basket.

========================================================================
===================        WHAT YOU NEED           =====================
========================================================================

* GNU/Linux 
   ( As paultag says: I'm sure you could get this to work with windows,
     but that's just all kinds of dumb. Don't use nonfree crap.
     PLUG: USE LINUX! IT WORKS GREAT! <3 LINUX			       )

* python-irclib
	 ( http://python-irclib.sourceforge.net/ 
	   Most distros: install python-irclib			       )
	
